data.description: Priced to sell. Location, Location Location! This floorplan won best use of space when it was built! Property is situated on an upgraded and large preserve on a quiet street for ultimate privacy.  Property features large primary bedroom and good size secondary bedrooms, Tons of closet and storage space.  New LVP flooring and carpet in 2021, Porch was re-screened and a new roof put on the porch in 2021, 2020 HVAC, 2019 new refrigerator and dishwasher, roof was installed in 2009 .Mere minutes to the vibrant Florida Beaches, Mayport Naval Station, Jacksonville's Town Center, Downtown, Restaurants and shopping  Property is ready for a quick move in!  Home has been virtually staged.
